		</ul></li><li class="level2"><a href="/media/videos/investors"><span>Videos</span></a></li><li class="level2 last"><a href="/media/media-contacts"><span>Media contacts</span></a></li>
	</ul></li><li class="level1 haschildren"><a href="/suppliers"><span>Suppliers</span></a><ul>
